\v 15 M…ôto n…ôsot…ôplan…ôn in m…ôm…ô r…ôhat…ômat kit t…®k…®m…®r, m…ôto in piat…ômat kit, k…ôn t…ôw…®r m…ôm…ô nakot…ôhgaiir lan.\x - \xo 3:15 \xt 1 Tes 5:14 \x*
\s1 Namnun n…ôghat…ôn
