\v 17 Io Pol, iatos pen mat…ôte …ôm e nelm…ôk n…ôghat…ôn u r…ôha n…ôn…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm it…ômat. K…ôn e naoa m…®n rafin ek…ôte n…ôhlan m…ôm…ô n…ôkot…®tun in naoa r…ôhak. Inu nol…ôn r…ôha n…ôte…ôn r…ôhak.
